{
  "stem": "12462.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in my sophomore year, I went to the University of Wisconsin and continued there until I graduated in 1934.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Letters and Science, the main campus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1934.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "BS, Bachelor of Science.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Economics and political science, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a large amount of history as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "College was very busy for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I became involved immediately in a lot of athletic as well as campus activities that didn't have anything to do with-- nothing directly to do with my studies.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was first on a basketball team at the college, the freshman basketball team.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and also on the second team of the football, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went to Wisconsin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was on the basketball, the second basketball team.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later I was on the Wisconsin crew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of the, the initiation into friendship with a couple of liberal pastors, Reverend Shorty Collins, Dr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Alfred W.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Swan, who was a congregationalist-- neither of these persons had the same religious background as I did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But both of them had a great influence on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was introduced to some other students who were liberal, and among other things there was quite a bit of prejudice on the campus by some of the Midwesterners.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of us decided we wanted to do something about that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a group of us who were pretty active on the campus formed a group called Koinos, K-O-I-N-O-S, which is a Greek word for 'in common.' And we didn't admit anybody to this group unless he was pretty well known on campus and unless he had a B average, he or she had a B average.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a result, we got quite a bit of attention, and we held meetings every three weeks or so, a luncheon meeting.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
